{"tid":725694,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"克羅地亞果球應唔應該全餐？","createTime":"2018-07-01T20:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T17:27:25.000Z","uid":16201,"like":423,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"98315b6f2e9bb0d46ff38acc0a548b0130169fa9","tid":725694,"uid":16201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T20:51:40.000Z","msg":"The previous 'triple-punishment' rule required a red card - and therefore a suspension - as well as the award of a penalty under those circumstances. However, players committing accidental fouls that deny a goalscoring chance will now be cautioned instead. <span style=\"color: red;\">But deliberate fouls will still incur a red card</span>.<br />\nApr 14, 2016<br />\n<br />\n空門100%既入波從後剷都唔算deliberate foul?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  12碼+黃牌"},{"pid":"4db05bf8588da91af4873ec5e293e93e3cca0a6f","tid":725694,"uid":40735,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T20:53:31.000Z","msg":"之前哥倫比亞對日本嗰場都全餐啦<br />\n咁樣空門單刀有乜理由唔係全餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2d4baba5e0f7a980f318e8968c6ce18391969f","tid":725694,"uid":56649,"like":1,"dislike":62,"score":-61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T20:54:03.000Z","msg":"黃牌都無張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f57e275846d25188b1c1e2d1042afb6a1465288","tid":725694,"uid":25825,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff2d4baba5e0f7a980f318e8968c6ce18391969f","tid":725694,"uid":56649,"like":1,"dislike":62,"score":-61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T20:54:03.000Z","msg":"黃牌都無張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T20:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s