":"其實十二碼都應該入硬既。。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"邊個話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n必入球定義係空門<br />\n十二碼有人守龍點算係空門<br />\n尋晚克vs丹嘅12碼大戰都救走好多球"},{"pid":"9c0a0015bdb98afcf9eeacc4c59fa34f844b3a38","tid":725694,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de3e743cb1c96411a2f9be2a0bd40cb239c0a2b9","tid":725694,"uid":85839,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n你有睇直播<br />\n見到球員都係激動左一下 <br />\n之後都無事<br />\n好專重球證既決定<br />\n甚至比人鏟跌個個都覺得落鏟落得好啱<br />\n因為大家都心知 個下唔鏟就輸尻硬<br />\n落鏟先有一線生機<br />\n而代價就係直紅加十二碼<br />\n根本在場所有人都接受呢個判決<br />\n嘈咩尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"咁咪即係合理化不君子行為囉<br />\n即係有人貪污，你唔講我唔講<br />\n對其他人又冇影響<br />\n所以就唔犯法，由得佢囉，係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68229ebfb27eaaf4ca1bf6a1f97a808729aa287","tid":725694,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98315b6f2e9bb0d46ff38acc0a548b0130169fa9","tid":725694,"uid":16201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T20:51:40.000Z","msg":"The previous 'triple-punishment' rule required a red card - and therefore a suspension - as well as the award of a penalty under those circumstances. However, players committing accidental fouls that deny a goalscoring chance will now be cautioned instead. <span style=\"color: red;\">But deliberate fouls will still incur a red card</span>.<br />\nApr 14, 2016<br />\n<br />\n空門100%既入波從後剷都唔算deliberate foul?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  12碼+黃牌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:03:04.000Z","msg":"Why read the rules from the news when the law itself is published online ...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.theifab.com/laws/fouls-and-misconduct/chapters/disciplinary-action\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theifab.com%2Flaws%2Ffouls-and-misconduct%2Fchapters%2Fdisciplinary-action&d=PFaxMuxMHjzFn7eH8WvPZcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1261771e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.theifab.com/laws/fouls-and-misconduct/chapters/disciplinary-action</a><br />\n<br />\nDENYING A GOAL OR AN OBVIOUS GOAL-SCORING OPPORTUNITY<br />\n<br />\nWhere a player denies the opposing team a goal or an obvious goal-scoring opportunity by a deliberate handball offence the player is sent off wherever the offence occurs.<br />\n<br />\nWhere a player commits an offence against an opponent within their own penalty area which denies an opponent an obvious goal-scoring opportunity and the referee awards a penalty kick, <span style=\"color: gold;\">the offender is cautioned if the offence was an attempt to play the ball</span>;<span style=\"color: red;\"> in all other circumstances (e.g. holding, pulling, pushing, no possibility to play the ball etc.) the offending player must be sent off</span>. A player, sent off player, substitute or substituted player who enters the field of play without the required referee&rsquo;s permission and interferes with play or an opponent and denies the opposing team a goal or an obvious goal-scoring opportunity is guilty of a sending-off offence."}]}